1959;;The Last Angry Man;;American;;Daniel Mann;;Paul Muni, David Wayne;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Last_Angry_Man;;As the fiercely dedicated general practitioner who tries to help the sick, the poor and the unfortunate in his decrepit neighborhood, Dr. Sam Abelman is a testy old man who faces life without compromise and Woodrow Thrasher is a troubled television executive fighting to preserve his career.